PrecisAppointment of JOSEPH WILLIAM POTTER, of Cumberland, Ontario, as a Deputy Chairperson of the Public Service Staff Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending April 13, 2001, and order that JOSEPH WILLIAM POTTER shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act.
